The suggestive comment of Pipe Bueno to Jessi Uribe for his intimate parts that unleashed teasing
Given the particular comment users questioned the sexual orientation of Pipe Bueno.

05 Nov 2019

As usual, the popular music singer Jessi Uribe, shares with his followers on social networks part of his busy schedule in the middle of the events during the weekends, on this occasion, he published a photograph of his concert in Cali in which He expresses all his love to the attendees.
However, who took all the attention in the publication was his colleague Pipe Bueno, who with a particular comment, in which he referred to the intimate parts of the Uribe, unleashed laughter and all kinds of comments among Internet users.
‚ÄúDaddy you were with that tight package, right? ü§£ü§£ Hehehe you had the girls in the boxes looking short .... hahaha, ‚Äùwas the suggestive comment of Pipe referring to the tight outfit that Uribe decided to use for his presentation in Cali.



Of course the comments did not wait, some laughing for the "imprudence" of the singer, while others took the opportunity to question him for his sexual orientation when looking at the "package" of his colleague.
